item.title: Khoisan
item.description: The Khoisan remained genetically and culturally distinct…The Khoisan are so distinct that by most estimates other Africans like Nigerian Yoruba are actually genetically closer to Eurasians (and Australians and Amerindians) than they are to the Khoisan.
